rComments: Tough class, but if you do the hw you will be fine.  His tests are different than anyother econ 302 tests, but they are not that hard.  Make sure you do over the homework before each test and you will get a B forsure if not an A.
Pretty tough class no matter who you have.  Grades are very fair.

This dude is very disorganized and doesnt know how to teach. The concepts are not very hard, but he just cant explain them in a clear way. He's not that hard of a grader though. He has a poor attitude, If you go to office hours he acts like you are inconveniencing him.

Hard teacher. Only homework is problems in back of book, and you will never get an answer for those. He is disorganized and frenzied. Tests have questions on them that you've never even seen before in class or the book. Prepare to fail!!
